@startuml UC-05_View_Profile

title UC-05: View User Profile - Sequence Diagram

skinparam SequenceArrowThickness 2
skinparam SequenceArrowColor #1976D2
skinparam ActorBackgroundColor #E3F2FD
skinparam ParticipantBackgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam SequenceGroupBackgroundColor #FFF9C4

actor User
participant Frontend
participant "API Gateway" as API
participant FirebaseService
participant Database as DB

User -> Frontend: 1. Click Profile/Settings
Frontend -> API: 2. GET /api/v1/users/profile
API -> FirebaseService: 3. get_user_profile(user_id)
FirebaseService -> DB: 4. Fetch user document
DB --> FirebaseService: 5. User data + profile
FirebaseService -> DB: 6. Fetch subscription
DB --> FirebaseService: 7. Subscription details
FirebaseService -> DB: 8. Fetch usage stats
DB --> FirebaseService: 9. Usage data
FirebaseService --> API: 10. Return complete user object
API --> Frontend: 11. 200 OK + user profile
Frontend --> User: 12. Display profile page

@enduml
